<h2>Collaborations</h2>
<div class="container mt-2">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-0 col-md-3 col-lg-3 col-xl-3">
            <Image
            class="img-thumbnail"
            src={codyops}
            alt="CodyOps"
            ></Image>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-9 col-lg-9 col-xl-8">
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li><h5>Senior GCP DevOps Consultant</h5></li>
                <li>October 2023 - Present</li>
                <li>Uruguay (Remote)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p>
      Started this project in GCP from scratch with the premise to only use GCP for everything. After our kick-off meeting, I designed all the infrastructure and coded with Terraform. Using Load Balancer with Backend Bucket for static content and Backend Service for dynamic content served from Google Serverless Functions. Using YouTube for video hosting, now migration to on-premise solution with an improved backend.
    </p>
</div>
<div class="container mt-2">
