        </div>
    </div>
    <p>
        Designed and implemented in AWS all new OpenShift Stacks. We used AWS CloudFormation to code all the infrastructure design and replicated this same to all regions where the company operates. With multiple apps running everywhere, we managed to migrate all these first to Docker, then to OpenShift. We also migrate all the manual processes to Jenkins Pipelines to fully integrated CI/CD in their building process.
