        Lead a team (50) as VP of Engineering, my focus in this new journey was more on project management and commercial. I work back to back with customers offering our best solutions for their needs and conducting a sustainable development effort in the team. This Management Role was a complete change for me and really challenging. I was able to work on many projects at same time doing focus on PKI. 
